content.summary: A software developer with over 1+ years of experience in the industry, currently working at Sparkfun Software Solution Bengaluru. Strong skills in software development life cycle, architecting scalable platforms, Object oriented programming, design and agile, scrum methodologies. Proficient in Python, Django, HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, JavaScript, and Git. Effective communicator with excellent interpersonal and problem-solving skills.
